---
import Eyebrow from './Eyebrow.astro';
---

<section>
  <div class="wrap">
    <Eyebrow label="What This Is" />
    <div class="explainer">
      <p>
        Renting a GPU now costs between $0.78 and $5.88 per hour depending on
        the chip and where you rent it. GPU Markets publishes the daily
        reference price across every major rental venue — so anyone building
        on, investing in, or reporting on AI infrastructure can see what
        compute actually costs today, and how that price has moved.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
